data.description: Owner Financing 10% down/30 year hold no prepayment penalty. Enjoy a quiet country like setting with all the comforts of suburban living. Top rated schools close by. Come see this amazing community and newly built home ready for a new family. Open floorplan with luxury vinyl flooring in all wet areas and carpet in the bedrooms. Granite countertops in both kitchen and bath. Gas appliances and sprinkler system front and back. Stainless Refrigerator and Washer & Dryer Convey. Super low energy bills with LOW E windows and LED lighting throughout the home. Prime location easy access to IH10 and 1604 or IH 35. 7min from Randolph AFB or FT Sam. Easy community to Austin or Downtown San Antonio 45-50 min either direction E or West. All information is deemed reliable and accurate; however, it is subject to independent verification by the buyer or buyer's representation
